title: Manfrotto Aluminum Fluid Monopod MVM250A - Overview
description:
Manfrotto Aluminum Fluid Monopod - MVM250A
http://www.abt.com/product/95133/Manfrotto-MVM250A.html

The MVM250A is a fluid video monopod that features a patented system using a fluid cartridge incorporated into the base that gives an incredibly smooth and judder-free panning action to the monopod when shooting video. Great compactness when folded thanks to its three retractable feet.
Specifications:
• Closed length: 67 cm
• Color: black color
• Material: aluminum
• Maximum working: temperature 60 °C
• Minimum working: temperature -10 °C
• Safety Payload Weight: 17.64 Lbs
• Leg sections: 4 number
